Just like the Trekker Mat, the Trekker Compact Mat has unique styling design and color combination that sets the Trekker Mats apart from the competition. Self-Inflating Mats not only provide a little extra comfort sleeping on top of rocks and other hard surfaces but also help to add a barrier between you and the cold ground beneath. A great solution for those looking for a lightweight, compact and reliable three quarter mat to take with them pretty much anywhere. The Trekker Compact Mat can also make a great small mat to use for physical training to be used with various exercises like sit-ups, crunches, etc. The Trekker Compact Mat is reversible with Olive on one side and Coyote on the opposite site.
